snippet.title: Famicom Disk System - Pro Golfer Saru - Kage no Tournament (1987)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Pro Golfer Saru is a Sports game, developed by TOSE and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 1987.
